<plot>Nick, a failure at life, is finally confronted by Knuckles, a dirty loan shark who demands the return of his money or else he will cut off Nick's precious finger. Only given a day to pay him back, Nick seeks the help of his obtuse brother Craig whose brilliant new scheme is impersonating police officers, commonly known as "Blue Light Bandits." When a lone detective discovers their greedy ploy they are forced to flee as fugitives and reconcile their differences as brothers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?076396</url></doc>
